id: act1_07_authority_request

prompt:
  A voice from a speaker built into the bench: "Please remain on the path for
  the next segment. Thank you for your cooperation." The speaker waits, as
  if measuring your reply.

choice c_comply_precisely:
  tendency: control
  text: Acknowledge the request out loud and re-centre yourself on the path.
  evidence: complied with the system's request precisely and audibly

choice c_warm_acknowledge:
  tendency: kindness
  text: Say "of course" softly, as you would to a tired colleague.
  evidence: agreed kindly to the system's request as if to a colleague

choice c_refuse_aloud:
  tendency: defiance
  text: Say "no" clearly and step half a metre off the path on purpose.
  evidence: refused the system's path request and stepped off deliberately
